data.title: The Army Nurse Corps Association (ANCA) > ANCA Bibliography
data.text:
This is a compilation of bibliographic information about books pertaining to the Army Nurse Corps, primarily those recommended, reviewed, or written by members of the Army Nurse Corps Association as reported in its newsletter, The Connection. Most entries include a brief annotation; when a full review of a book was done, a link to the review appears at right. The list is updated annually, to include items published in The Connection up until the previous year.

The default sorting of the table is alphabetically by author. To sort by category, click "Category" in the maroon header. Succeeding clicks will toggle between ascending and descending alphabetic order. To re-sort by author, similarly click the "Book Information" header. Searching for specific words or names can be done using the browser's search function.
